<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Japanese_name&amp;action=edit&amp;section=16" title="Edit section: External links">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">External links</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.sljfaq.org/afaq/names.html" class="external text" title="http://www.sljfaq.org/afaq/names.html" rel="nofollow">Japanese names section</a> of <a href="http://www.sljfaq.org/afaq/afaq.html" class="external text" title="http://www.sljfaq.org/afaq/afaq.html" rel="nofollow">sci.lang.japan FAQ</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.japanorama.com/namesinj.html" class="external text" title="http://www.japanorama.com/namesinj.html" rel="nofollow">Japanorama: Japanese Names</a></li>
<li><span class="languageicon" style="font-size:0.95em; font-weight:bold; color:#555;">(Japanese)</span><a href="http://web.archive.org/web/20060518234359/http://www.kokemus.kokugo.juen.ac.jp/names/namae/NA-index.html" class="external text" title="http://web.archive.org/web/20060518234359/http://www.kokemus.kokugo.juen.ac.jp/names/namae/NA-index.html" rel="nofollow">「日本人の名前」目次(Index page of "Names of Japanese")(Internet Archive)</a> Japanese names in Kanji and Hiragana.</li>
<li><span class="languageicon" style="font-size:0.95em; font-weight:bold; color:#555;">(Japanese)</span><a href="http://www2s.biglobe.ne.jp/~suzakihp/index40.html" class="external text" title="http://www2s.biglobe.ne.jp/~suzakihp/index40.html" rel="nofollow">全国の苗字（名字）１０万種掲載("Publication of 100,000 surnames(names) in the country")</a></li>
<li><span class="languageicon" style="font-size:0.95em; font-weight:bold; color:#555;">(Japanese)</span><a href="http://www.ipc.shizuoka.ac.jp/~jjksiro/shiro.html" class="external text" title="http://www.ipc.shizuoka.ac.jp/~jjksiro/shiro.html" rel="nofollow">静岡大学人文学部 城岡研究室(" Shirōka Lab of the Department of Humanities in the Shizuoka University")</a> surnames of Japan, Shizuoka prefecture, Okinawa prefecture and Germany.</li>
<li><span class="languageicon" style="font-size:0.95em; font-weight:bold; color:#555;">(Japanese)</span><a href="http://www.myshop.co.jp/japancal/fname/name.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.myshop.co.jp/japancal/fname/name.htm" rel="nofollow">名字見聞録("Records of names")</a> Japanese names in Kanji and Hiragana.</li>
<li><span class="languageicon" style="font-size:0.95em; font-weight:bold; color:#555;">(Japanese)</span><a href="http://park14.wakwak.com/~myj/" class="external text" title="http://park14.wakwak.com/~myj/" rel="nofollow">苗字舘("Museum of surnames)"</a> statistics of Japanese surnames.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.aboutnames.ch/japanese.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.aboutnames.ch/japanese.htm" rel="nofollow">Japanese Given Names</a></li>
<li>Popular <a href="http://www.japanese-name-translation.com/site/japanese_baby_names.html" class="external text" title="http://www.japanese-name-translation.com/site/japanese_baby_names.html" rel="nofollow">Japanese baby names</a> 1994 to 2003.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.csse.monash.edu.au/cgi-bin/cgiwrap/jwb/wwwjdic?3C" class="external text" title="http://www.csse.monash.edu.au/cgi-bin/cgiwrap/jwb/wwwjdic?3C" rel="nofollow">WWWJDIC</a> online dictionary with over 400,000 Japanese names.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.kobe-np.co.jp/kobenews/sougou/021124ke84630.html" class="external text" title="http://www.kobe-np.co.jp/kobenews/sougou/021124ke84630.html" rel="nofollow">男子も「さん」で... 「君」廃止、学校で広がる</a></li>
</ul>
